iv><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-6 gf_col-md-6 gf_col-sm-6 gf_col-xs-6" id="c-1685527753840" data-id="1685527753840"><div data-label="Row" data-key="row" data-atomgroup="row" id="r-1709741729763" class="gf_row" data-icon="gpicon-row" data-id="1709741729763"><div class="gf_column gf_col-lg-12 gf_col-md-12 gf_col-sm-12 gf_col-xs-12" id="c-1685525993283" data-id="1685525993283"><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741729721" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1709741729721" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/46cf84b6-abd2-4878-b7f3-d1ee390a2256/x-circle.svg" alt="" class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" data-width="24px" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="24" natural-height="25" width="24" height="25" loading="lazy"></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741729753" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1709741729753"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-center-lg gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-sm" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><span style="color: rgb(108, 182, 76);">Kundenfragen beantwortet: Alles, was Sie über den TurboClean wissen müssen:</span></h3></div></div><div data-label="Accordion" data-key="accordion" data-atomgroup="module" id="m-1709741729758" class="module-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-accordion" data-ver="2" data-id="1709741729758"><div data-accordion-group="" class="module " data-opendefault="1" data-opentab="1" data-single="1" data-bordercolor="#cecece" data-bordersize="1px"><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="1" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1709741729758-1" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1709741729758-1" data-ver="1"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">F: Welche Power hat der TurboClean?</span></p><p></p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: #FFFFFF"><article data-index="1" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741729781" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709741729781"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Die Saugleistung Unterdruck für die Power Edition beträgt 19.000 Pa. Für die kleine Größe des Staubsaugers ist es ziemlich enorm und einmalig auf dem Markt. Sie erhalten ein kompaktes, handliches Gerät, welches zugleich eine sehr starke Saugleistung hat.</p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="2" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1709741729758-2" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1709741729758-2" data-ver="1"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">F: Wie lange hält der Akku?</span></p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: #FFFFFF"><article data-index="2" data-key="content1" class="item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1709741729778" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1709741729778"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Bei einer durchgehenden Nutzung hält der Akku bis zu 30 Minuten. Erfahrungsgemäß fallen jedoch die Reinigungsintervalle kürzer aus und der Staubsauger wird nie 30 Minuten am Stück eingesetzt. Das heißt, Sie können den TurboClean problemlos über mehrere Tage nutzen ohne diesen jedesmal aufzuladen.</p><p></p></div></div></article></div></div><div data-accordion="" style="padding-bottom: "><div data-control="" data-index="3" data-key="content" class="chevron iCon-right text- item-content"><div data-label="Text Block" id="e-1709741729758-3" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-id="1709741729758-3" data-ver="1"><div class="elm text-edit gf_gs-text-paragraph-1 gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-exc=""><p><span style="font-weight: bold;">F: Wie laut ist der TurboClean Handstaubsauger?</span></p><p></p></div></div><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button><button type="button" class="wrapp-icon"><span class="acc-icon" style="background-color:#000000"></span></button></div><div data-content="" style="margin-top: ; background-color: #FFFFFF"><article data-index="3" data-key="content1" class="item-cont